The accident happened on Thursday night in Awasi town, 42km (26 miles) away from Kisumu. The bus was heading to the capital city, Nairobi. The regional police head Benson Maweu is quoted as saying the driver of the bus tried to overtake a tractor and crashed into an oncoming truck. Pictures of the accident show the mangled wreckage of the bus.
--bbc-- 13 PEOPLE dead following 1.30am crash involving an Eldoret Express bus from Kisumu and a truck at Pala area near Awasi. pic.twitter.com/FvWwyO64Aa